code: @Override protected BufferedReader openReader(Path logFile) {     assumeFalse("Skipping test because it is being run against an external cluster.", logFile.getFileName().toString().equals("--external--")).     return AccessController.doPrivileged((PrivilegedAction<BufferedReader>) () -> {         try {             return Files.newBufferedReader(logFile, StandardCharsets.UTF_8).         } catch (IOException e) {             throw new RuntimeException(e).         }     }). }
